name: Recycled Picket Fence Dining Table
description: A custom 2m long dining table in the finishing stages for Bin 3 - Fine Wine Merchants in Balwyn. This dining table is made almost completely out of Reclaimed and Recycled Wood. Table top made is from old cypress pine picket fence palings rescued from a house demolition in Coburg North. The table legs were sourced from a broken table at Darebin Resource Recovery Centre. Complete with coffee stained edging. 90% Recycled Timber 10% New New pine sourced from renewable plantations. The varnish is water based, high performance and environmentally friendly. GET IN CONTACT if you'd like a similar custom made dining table for your place.

name: Recycled Garden Lattice Dining Table - Small
description: Small dining table for your small apartment or small home space. Lightweight and fresh. Made out of recycled garden lattice and wood flooring, sourced from a house renovation in Preston. The varnish is water based, high performance and environmentally friendly. Legs also new as requested by the client. GET IN CONTACT if you'd like a similar table made for your place.
